---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started - AppFrames Documentation">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <div class="docs-container">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <nav>
          <h3>Guides</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/docs/getting-started" class="active">Getting Started</a></li>
            <li><a href="/docs/creating-mockups">Creating Mockups</a></li>
            <li><a href="/docs/templates">Templates</a></li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Reference</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/docs/api">API Reference</a></li>
            <li><a href="/docs/features">Features</a></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="back-to-docs">
            <a href="/docs">‚Üê Back to Docs</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </aside>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Getting Started</h1>
        
        <p>Welcome to AppFrames! This guide will help you get up and running quickly with creating beautiful app screenshots and mockups.</p>
        
        <h2>Installation</h2>
        <p>AppFrames is available for macOS and can be downloaded from:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Mac App Store</strong>: <a href="#">Download from App Store</a></li>
          <li><strong>TestFlight</strong>: <a href="#">Join Beta Testing</a></li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>First Steps</h2>
        
        <h3>1. Launch AppFrames</h3>
        <p>After installation, launch AppFrames from your Applications folder or Launchpad.</p>
        
        <h3>2. Create a New Project</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Click "New Project" on the welcome screen</li>
          <li>Choose a template or start with a blank canvas</li>
          <li>Select your preferred device frame</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h3>3. Import Your Screenshots</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Drag and drop your app screenshots into AppFrames</li>
          <li>Or use File > Import to browse for images</li>
          <li>AppFrames supports PNG, JPEG, and other common formats</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>4. Customize Your Layout</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Position your screenshots within the device frames</li>
          <li>Add text, backgrounds, and other elements</li>
          <li>Use the layer panel to organize your content</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>5. Export Your Mockup</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Click File > Export</li>
          <li>Choose your desired format and resolution</li>
          <li>Save your finished mockup</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2>Next Steps</h2>
        <p>Now that you've created your first mockup, explore these advanced features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/docs/templates">Templates and Layouts</a></li>
          <li><a href="/docs/creating-mockups">Advanced Mockup Techniques</a></li>
          <li><a href="/docs/features">Feature Reference</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }
  
  .sidebar {
    background: #f8fafc;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    height: fit-content;
  }
  
  .sidebar nav h3 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  .sidebar nav h3:not(:first-child) {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .sidebar ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .sidebar li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .sidebar a {
    color: #6b7280;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    display: block;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  
  .sidebar a:hover,
  .sidebar a.active {
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .back-to-docs {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
  
  .back-to-docs a {
    color: #3b82f6;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  
  .content {
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  
  .content h1 {
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .content h2 {
    color: #111827;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .content h3 {
    color: #374151;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .content p,
  .content li {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .content ul,
  .content ol {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .content a {
    color: #3b82f6;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .docs-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    
    .sidebar {
      order: 2;
    }
  }
</style>